---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout>
	<main class="min-h-screen text-slate-950 pb-24" style="background-color: var(--color-bg)">
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-16">
			<a href={`${base}/`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
				Back to home
			</a>
			<div class="rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/5 backdrop-blur">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: June 2026</p>

				<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">1. Introduction</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">Welcome to Voyaflair.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					At Voyaflair, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy
					Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, how we protect it, and the rights you have
					regarding your personal data.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					By using this website, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">2. Information We Collect</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We may collect information that you voluntarily provide, as well as certain information that is automatically
					collected when you visit the website.
				</p>
				<h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Information You Provide Voluntarily</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">This may include:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Your name</li>
					<li>Your email address</li>
					<li>Information submitted through contact forms</li>
					<li>Information submitted through newsletter subscriptions</li>
					<li>Information submitted through comments</li>
					<li>Any other information you voluntarily choose to provide</li>
				</ul>
				<h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Information Collected Automatically</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					When you visit the website, certain information may be collected automatically, including:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>IP address</li>
					<li>Browser type</li>
					<li>Device type</li>
					<li>Operating system</li>
					<li>Pages viewed</li>
					<li>Time spent on pages</li>
					<li>Referring website</li>
					<li>General geographic location</li>
					<li>Website interaction data</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">We may use collected information to:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Operate and maintain the website</li>
					<li>Improve website performance and user experience</li>
					<li>Respond to inquiries and messages</li>
					<li>Send newsletters and updates</li>
					<li>Provide requested information</li>
					<li>Analyze website traffic</li>
					<li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>
					<li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
					<li>Improve content and services</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">4. Newsletter Communications</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If you voluntarily subscribe to the Voyaflair newsletter, we may use your email address to send:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Travel articles</li>
					<li>Destination guides</li>
					<li>Travel tips</li>
					<li>Website updates</li>
					<li>Promotional content</li>
					<li>Affiliate recommendations</li>
					<li>Special announcements</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					You may unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link included in every email or by contacting us
					directly.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">5. Contact Forms</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					When you contact us through forms on the website, we collect the information you choose to provide.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We use this information solely for the purpose of responding to your inquiry and maintaining communication
					related to your request.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">6. Comments</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If commenting functionality is available, we may collect information submitted through comments, including:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Name</li>
					<li>Email address</li>
					<li>IP address</li>
					<li>Browser information</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					This information may be used for moderation, spam prevention, security, and community management purposes.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We reserve the right to moderate, edit, or remove comments at our discretion.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">7. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair uses cookies and similar technologies to improve website functionality, analyze traffic, remember
					preferences, support affiliate partnerships, and support advertising services.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Additional information regarding cookies can be found in our
					<a href={`${base}/cookie-policy`} class="font-medium text-slate-900 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-slate-700">Cookie Policy</a>.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">8. Analytics</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We may use analytics services to better understand how visitors interact with our website.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Analytics providers may collect information such as:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Visited pages</li>
					<li>Time spent on pages</li>
					<li>Device information</li>
					<li>Browser information</li>
					<li>Approximate geographic location</li>
					<li>Traffic sources</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					This information helps us improve the website and user experience.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">9. Affiliate Programs</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">Voyaflair may participate in affiliate marketing programs.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					When visitors click affiliate links, affiliate partners may use cookies or tracking technologies to track
					referrals and attribute commissions.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">This does not increase the price paid by visitors.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Affiliate tracking is governed by the policies of the respective affiliate partners.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">10. Advertising</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair may display advertisements through third-party advertising networks.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Advertising providers may use cookies, pixels, and similar technologies to:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Deliver advertisements</li>
					<li>Measure performance</li>
					<li>Improve relevance</li>
					<li>Prevent fraud</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					These providers may collect information according to their own privacy policies.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">11. Third-Party Services</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">We may use third-party services to operate and improve the website.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Examples may include:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Analytics providers</li>
					<li>Email marketing providers</li>
					<li>Comment management services</li>
					<li>Advertising providers</li>
					<li>Affiliate platforms</li>
					<li>Hosting providers</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					These third parties may process data according to their own privacy policies.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">12. Data Retention</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We retain personal information only for as long as necessary to:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Fulfill the purposes described in this Policy</li>
					<li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
					<li>Resolve disputes</li>
					<li>Enforce agreements</li>
					<li>Maintain security and operational integrity</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">13. Data Security</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We take reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational measures to protect personal information from
					unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, misuse, or destruction.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					However, no method of data transmission or storage can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">14. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Depending on your location and applicable laws, you may have the right to:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Access your personal data</li>
					<li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
					<li>Request deletion of your data</li>
					<li>Restrict processing</li>
					<li>Object to processing</li>
					<li>Withdraw consent</li>
					<li>Request data portability</li>
					<li>Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">15. GDPR Rights for European Visitors</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If you are located within the European Economic Area (EEA), we process personal data in accordance with
					applicable data protection laws, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">You have the right to:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Access your personal data</li>
					<li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
					<li>Request erasure of your data</li>
					<li>Restrict processing</li>
					<li>Object to processing</li>
					<li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
					<li>Request a copy of your personal data</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">16. Children's Privacy</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">Voyaflair is not directed toward children under the age of 13.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If we become aware that personal information has been collected from a child without appropriate consent, we
					will take steps to remove such information.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">17. International Data Transfers</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Information collected through the website may be processed or stored in countries outside your country of
					residence.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					By using the website, you acknowledge that data may be transferred and processed in accordance with applicable
					laws and safeguards.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">18. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Any changes will be posted on this page, and the updated version will become effective upon publication.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">19. Contact Information</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your privacy rights, please contact:
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7">
					<a href="mailto:voyaflair@gmail.com" class="font-medium text-slate-900 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-slate-700">voyaflair@gmail.com</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>
